      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAPER SHREDDER (6) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 22.33 with a one length win at Gosford over 388m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can make it two on the bounce. WOOLGOOLGA LASS (4) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at Bulli in a handy 19.35 beating Scott Quibble. Has good early speed so she should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Form should stack up. MAGIC WYLDE (8) chased the lead early from the inside and boxed on well to finish second, beaten 0.8 lengths (22.67) at this track in a Mix 2/3 over 400m. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Winning chance. BUMPY BLUE (3) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
